# Build context is the monorepo root (see apps/storefront/Dockerfile).
# Keep it small and never ship secrets or local build artifacts.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.medusa
**/.astro
**/.turbo
**/.git
**/.vscode
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log

# Secrets: PUBLIC_* values are passed as build args, never via .env files.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
